Model
  - class
  
Field
  - atributes in columns
  
Type of field 
   - determine the type of data ex:EmailField, DateField
   - refer : https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.1/ref/models/fields/
   
 Field Option
   - every field have certain resriction - like max 50 char
   - restrictions are defined by field option ex: null , blank, CharField
   - refer : https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.1/ref/models/fields/
   
  Syntax:
******************************************************
from django.db import models
class customer (model.Model):
  first_name = models.Charfield ( max_lenght = 30 )
  last_name = models.charfield ( min_lenght = 10 )
******************************************************
      
      Here class : model
           first_name, last_name : fields
           Char_field : Field type
           Field option : Restriction max_lenght = 30
           
           
